name: CoreAPI Testing_Run
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Testing_Run API Details.
about:
Description

Planet 9-Testing_Run maintains the overview list of all test run cases.

API_Testing_Run is the API to access the test run cases, and the operations performed on them.

Operations Performed 

List

Get the list of the test

ResponseList - Definition

Get

Get the selected test details

RequestID
ResponseGet-Definition

Del

Delete the selected test

RequestID               

Save

Save the test

RequestSave
ResponseGet-Definition
